<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
								
	<p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
	<p n="1-6">For this Cattaperumāṉ<note>That is, most probably, a form of Śiva. See MTL, s.v. <foreign>cattaṉ</foreign>: <quote>2. (Śaiva.) The formless Šiva, as the embodiment of energy</quote>.</note>,
	what Maticūtabhaṭṭar gave <supplied reason="subaudible">is</supplied>:
	<list>
		<item>one <foreign>mā</foreign> of land, in Kumārapaṭṭi, for sacred food-offerings,</item>
		<item>and one <foreign>kaḻañcu</foreign> of gold for a glorious lamp.</item>
	</list>
	</p>	
	
</div>
	
